2. Block Selection from Dictionary:

- Block #1 (arch/curved base block) - 2 copies
- Block #10 (cube/rectangular block)
- Block #11 and/or #15 (angled/triangular top blocks)

3. Assembly Instructions:

    Step1: Move block #1 (left arch support)
    Step2: Move block #1 (right arch support)
    Step3: Move block #10 (center rectangular block)

}
